cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.DL

The paper discusses the use of computer methods for analyzing histological images, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of convolutional neural networks (cs.LG) and deep learning (cs.DL) for segmentation. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of morphometric criteria (cs.MM) for quantitative diagnostic methods. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely for this paper.
